(1011, 'Asmalair 10mg 10 tab.', 'ازمالير 10مجم 10 قرص', '', '40', 'Montelukast', 'Hi-pharm', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '10mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
